207.roomDescription: Setting foot on this platform seems to lower the fog in the area allowing you to see the massive bestial humanoid statues to either side of a large circular entrance. The entrance itself seems to have been sealed shut, and there seems to be no slot for a key of any kind.

moves.moveDescription: Stepping away from the platform seemingly gives signal to the fog to rush back in. Sadly it seems like traversal of the area is going to continue being difficult.
